You should not have
gone in there.

45
00:08:14,225 --> 00:08:17,968
Lockwood has stumbled into
the end of a strange story...

46
00:08:19,986 --> 00:08:24,689
a story that began
30 years before

47
00:08:24,723 --> 00:08:27,309
when an old man returned
to Wuthering Heights...

48
