49
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,872
He's coming!

50
00:08:49,911 --> 00:08:51,155
Joseph.

51
00:08:51,191 --> 00:08:53,133
All right, don't rush me.

52
00:08:55,928 --> 00:08:57,073
Father!

53
00:08:57,112 --> 00:08:58,868
Ah, home again, Cathy.

54
00:08:58,904 --> 00:09:00,792
