of the open moor.

81
00:10:35,655 --> 00:10:38,689
The rock and the lowering skies.

82
00:10:38,727 --> 00:10:40,615
Oh, mercifuI God,

83
00:10:40,648 --> 00:10:42,819
Father of our Lord
Jesus Christ...

84
