131
00:14:37,515 --> 00:14:40,483
I was thinking about the sea.

132
00:14:41,868 --> 00:14:43,013
You ever seen the sea?

133
00:14:43,052 --> 00:14:44,000
No, I was too little.

134
00:14:44,043 --> 00:14:45,288
I don't remember.

135
00:14:46,765 --> 00:14:48,620
My life didn't begin
untiI I...

136
