when you were away.

260
00:25:09,194 --> 00:25:12,042
I waited every day
for a sight of you...

261
00:25:12,074 --> 00:25:13,667
coming over the moors.

262
00:25:14,955 --> 00:25:16,842
But you didn't come.

263
00:25:16,875 --> 00:25:19,242
So I put a wire mesh
over the nest,

264
00:25:19,275 --> 00:25:22,571
