died when they hatched.

265
00:25:22,603 --> 00:25:23,847
Why?

266
00:25:23,884 --> 00:25:25,029
Because the parent birds

267
00:25:25,067 --> 00:25:27,010
couldn't get near
enough to feed them.

268
00:25:27,052 --> 00:25:29,769
No. Why did you starve them?

269
00:25:29,805 --> 00:25:31,299
