I'd have spared them.

272
00:25:39,758 --> 00:25:42,126
In the future,
you must spare them.

273
00:25:48,879 --> 00:25:50,286
Don't you trust me?

274
00:25:53,488 --> 00:25:55,627
Don't you know
I'll always come back?

275
